35
00:01:12.100 --> 00:01:14.866
I just want more people to see your work

36
00:01:15.200 --> 00:01:16.166
How come?

37
00:01:16.166 --> 00:01:17.566
Do what you want

38
00:01:17.566 --> 00:01:19.100
Brother, I will never be angry with you.

39
00:01:19.100 --> 00:01:20.200
But speaking of

40
00:01:20.200 --> 00:01:22.766
You see, I was so ugly when I was a kid

41
00:01:22.766 --> 00:01:23.700
How come?

42
00:01:23.700 --> 00:01:26.300
In my heart, you have always been the most beautiful

